    ##################################################################
    # Musicline long format. (timepoint, voice, event type, event data)

0       0  marker introduction
0.5     1  note   F♭/D♯
1       2  rest
1.5     3  rested
10.50   4  tail
123.456 10 tempo  90    

    # Do not isolate (color) the backslash escape character when starting event data.

0     1 note \   Do not color \ characters in long format.
1     1 note \ \ Do not color \ characters in long format.
1.5   1 note \1  Do not color \ characters in long format.
10.50 1 note \\1 Do not color \ characters in long format.

    ##################################################################
    # Musicline short format. (timepoint, note data)

0
1 note
1.5 This note is F♭/D♯
10.50   Data with more than one space before.
123.456 Data with more than one space after.    

    # Do isolate (color) the backslash escape character when starting note data.

0     \   Only color the first \ character.
1     \ \ Only color the first \ character.
1     \ \
1.5   \1  Only color the first \ character.
10.50 \\1 Only color the first \ character.
10.50 \\

